title: Jazz Monthly - Part 10 - HQ - PDF
description:
Jazz Monthly - Part 10 - HQ - PDF


One issue of the UK magazine Jazz Monthly


Issue 187 - September 1970


The format of the magazine changed to glossy. All bitmap scan settings were maintained and the individual scanned pages were approximately the same megabytes size as previous issues. The compression settings in Adobe Acrobat X Pro were also maintained. The PDF output from Acrobat X Pro has resulted in a smaller file size.
